reviewText: This course gave me the ability to get started with Robotics.   There is much more to be learned, but this excellent course gave me the courage to buy my first Raspberry PI and get it working.   I would highly recommend this course.
I am so happy to join the course. Topic isn't simple, but the way it is presented really encouraged me to dive deeper.
